Imeslayen-agi « tikkelt nniḍen daɣen » sbeggnen-d belli ayen yețwaxelqen ad yenhezz ad yenger iwakken a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
Lemfaṣel n lǧețța iwumi ur nefki ara lqima, d nutni i nețḥadar akteṛ n wiyaḍ ; ihi d lemfaṣel ur nezmir ara a d-nebder i nețḥadar aṭas,
A lḥukkam d lecyux n wat Isṛail ! Imi ɣef lxiṛ i nexdem i wergaz-agi aɛiban d wamek i geḥla i ɣ-d-testeqsayem ass-agi,
Tamaṭ n tezṛaɣit deg umeslayt-nni, uɣanim i t-iɣummen aẓekka, deg waggur ur d-yețțawiḥt ara, tbuciḍant-nsent deg yiwet n tbuciḍant.
Am akken i tedṛa di tektabt n ?abur i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi si leṛwaḥ n wid iwumi yemmezlen tamurt n Jafa.
Mi d-yuli yiṭij, yezlef imɣan-nni dɣa qquṛen, imi izuṛan-nsen ur lqayit ara.
Lɛid i deg xedmen aɣṛum mbla iɣes n temtunt ițțusemman « Tafaska n izimer n leslak » tqeṛb-ed.
Tazzla deg wannar d ayen yelhan meɛna tenfeɛ i lǧețța kan, ma ṭṭaɛa n Sidi Ṛebbi tenfeɛ i kullec axaṭer deg-s i tella tudert n tura akk-d ț-țin i d-iteddun i ɣ-iwɛed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma yella nnejmaɛen imasiḥiyen meṛṛa deg yiwen wemkan, bdan țḥemmiden akk Sidi Ṛebbi s tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, ma kecmen-d yemdanen ur nessin ara ayagi neɣ wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, eɛni ur d-qqaṛen ara tedrewcem ?
Di yal tama n tmurt slan s lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i wen-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi : di tmurt-agi ur yekfeṛ ara, ayagi d ayen ur neǧhid ara di liman, ixuṣṣen di liman.
M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal tețțuɣal d ulac, meɛna m'ara d-teḥyu, a d-teḥyu s ccan d ameqqran. M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal teffeɣ-iț tezmert, m'ara d-teḥyu a d-teḥyu s lǧehd d ameqqran.
Dinna ara yilin yimeṭṭawen d nndama tameqqrant m'ara yeǧǧa Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin nniḍen.
Lḥakem yellan d aqeṛṛuy ɣef meyya iɛsekṛiyen akk-d iɛsekṛiyen iɛussen Sidna Ɛisa, tekcem-iten tugdi mi walan tergagi lqaɛa d wayen akk yedṛan.
Ma d win meqqren yezmer ad yečč ayen yeseḥḥan, imi i gjeṛṛeb, yessen ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri.
?ẓuɣṛen Sidna Ɛisa armi d yiwen n wemkan ițțusemman Luṭ si tmurt n Maṣeṛ, qqimet ɣuṛ-es iwakken ad yaɣ awal i yi-d-yellan di temdint n Diutya, iwakken a ten-iheggi abrid i lḥakem n tmurt n Ityubya.
ț-țuḥṛicin-nni, wwint-ed yid-sent tiqbucin n zzit.
Issefham-asen, ițbeggin-asen-d di Tira belli Lmasiḥ ilaq ad yeɛteb yerna a d-yessiweḍ lexbaṛ belli Ɛisa Lmasiḥ.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-agi,
Tafaska n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg wass n westeɛfu.
Tazwara, ilaq aț-țeẓrem belli deg ussan ineggura a d-kkren yemdanen ara iɛicen s lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen, yerna ad tmesxiṛen fell-awen ;
Tafaska n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg wass n westeɛfu. Tameddit n wass uqbel ass n westeɛfu, lecyux n wat Isṛail ur bɣin ara ad ǧǧen lǧețțat-nni ɣef yimidagen di leɛwaceṛ. Ṛuḥen ad ssutren i Bilaṭus a sen-ṛẓen iḍaṛṛen i widak-nni yețwasemmṛen ; iwakken ad kksen lǧețțat-nsen.
Imezdaɣ n lǧiha-nni meṛṛa ṛuḥen, awḍen-as-d iman-is d ameqqran. Mi d-nnejmaɛen, tebɛen abrid n Sidna Ɛisa.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. Refden amextaf n lbabuṛ, ṛuḥen rrif rrif n tegzirt n Kritus.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen. LLlan daɣen wid iḥeṛmen iman-nsen ɣef zwaǧ, ɣef ddemma n ddnubat-nsen.
Di tmurt-nni, llan imeksawen ițnusun di lexlawi, țɛassan lmal-nsen deg yiḍ.
Akken daɣen taṣebḥit, teqqaṛem a d-iwwet ugeffur ( lehwa ) axaṭer yella usigna. AAmek ! Tesnem aț-țfehmem lḥala n igenni, ur tezmirem ara aț-țfehmem licaṛat yeɛnan lweqt-agi !
